Barbara Rosenblat https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barbara_Rosenblat 0 Barbara Rosenblat (born 17 July 1950 in London, England) is a British actress and voice artist. She is a beloved narrator of audiobooks, famed for her performance of multiple voices and accents. She has also appeared on screen such as in the Netflix original series Orange Is the New Black as Miss Rosa.
